<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>لا شيء فيها ... ٣٩ ... ١<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>شاة ... ١٢٠ ... ٤٠<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
