<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>ثلاث شياه ... ٣٩٩ ... ٢٠١<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>أربع شياه ... ٤٩٩ ... ٤٠٠<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
